    "role": "assistant",
    "content": "Thought: 产品文档已成功写入 `/mnt/shared/design/product_spec.md`。下一步需向 Manager 发送 `task_done` 邮件，仅包含路径引用，不附全文。\nAction: send_mail\nAction Input: {\"to\": \"manager\", \"from\": \"pm\", \"type\": \"task_done\", \"subject\": \"产品文档已完成\", \"content\": \"产品文档已完成，路径：/mnt/shared/design/product_spec.md，请验收\"}\nObservation: {\"errcode\": 0, \"errmsg\": \"success\", \"msg_id\": \"a41a0cc0-8856-4d29-ad01-2a91fa837ded\"}"
